Welcome to the DLB documentation!
===================================

DLB is a collection of tools targeting HPC applications. 
Its main goal is to help with the dynamic load balancing of hybrid codes, which use a nested parallelism model.
Therefore, DLB provides components to modify ressources at runtime, as well as a profiler to gather performance metrics. 

.. note::
   If you are new here, consider having a look at the :ref:`overview` first.





